{"id": "1218189717728661544", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "意識潛遊全部都是主角進喚醒體的夢的情況。\n然後這不算穿越時空，更像是藉由夢境這種深入喚醒體潛意識的行為去稍微更改了他們的記憶。\n（詳情請見阿格里帕的意識潛遊", "timestamp": "2024-03-15T13:31:01.577000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
